  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dda \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9 \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0d92\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0db6\u0db3 \u0dc3\u0da7\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The items in the temple and the notes about them are lost",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior police officer said that the absence of log entries regarding the items in the media unit of Araliya Gaha Madura has seriously hampered the investigations.",
        "Laptop computers, video cameras and many valuable items were stolen",
        "The officer said that investigations are being conducted based on a complaint made by an officer of the media unit and the navy that some people have stolen items from the media unit.",
        "The senior police officer added that the militants had entered the Araliyagaha Mandir on the previous day and made holes in the media unit which had been set aside temporarily and made these thefts."
      ],
